column5: Im always perplexed when i see this stuff on the shelves lol. Im perplexed mainly because ive seen it for years now so they must be getting customers to buy into it,or it wouldnt have lasted this long. Even more confusing, is the bread and butter of the makers of this product, is actually egg cures.
